UPDATE companies SET agent_ids_notes = 'Founders and Key Team: Name – Title - Partha Prittam Nayak — CEO — Ex-Swiggy, Supr Daily, Nestaway; Led Operations & Growth; IIM Bangalore, NIT Rourkela; Focus: company strategy, operations and scale. - Rishabh Gupta — CPTO — Ex-Zepto, Equal, Navi; Built products for scale; IIT Bombay; Focus: product & technology leadership. Relevance of prior experience to problem being solved - Founding team combines growth/ops (delivery/assistance platforms) and scale-product experience, aligned with rapid expansion, SOP-driven execution, and tech-enabled operations.
Product and Technology: Product stage - Pilot / limited market test ongoing; no GA launch yet. Core functionality & tech stack - On-demand trained cooks with ingredient kits; centralized Mother Hub for kit creation; Dark Stores for inventory and fulfillment; Chef app for real-time guidance; barcode-based sourcing history; CV-based color/portion audits; time-tracking and real-time feedback. Unique IP - Kit-based standardization (pre-measured, vacuum-sealed ingredients) enabling high consistency; digital SOPs executed by cooks; barcode-tracing of ingredients; “Kit Moat” as a backbone for scale. Key differentiators vs substitutes - Faster, consistent home meals (40 minutes) with trained cooks; no grocery shopping; high hygiene trust; real-time adjustments (oil/salt/spices); strong emphasis on standardization and safety vs home-cook variability or pure restaurant delivery. Implementation complexity / switching costs - [Inference] ...' WHERE id = 381 AND (agent_ids_notes IS NULL OR agent_ids_notes = '');
