UPDATE companies SET agent_ids_notes = 'Notes:: 1. **Ankit & other CoFo Jayant** 1. Pissed off that students couldn’t take CS programs unless they did pre-reqs 1. Made a simple web tool to map out pre-reqs & simulate the pathways in future semester 1. 1 year together selling software to corporate training academies 1. Both were Tech CoFos hence no Sales muscle 1. **Abhishek** 1. Feb 2024 → Jayant and Abhishek wanted to do something together 1. Put everything on the line to built a business 1. Ankit has student loan 1. Jayant has left PPO 1. Tried to sell personal transcribing tool to founders 1. His dad has taken an unsecured biz loan at 48% p.a. 1. **Problem → multi lingual conversations in Indian call center** 1. Spammed everyone on LinkedIn 1. Jazib Ali from Slice → collections team is 300 versus CX team is 30 1. Sometimes caller goes beyond boundaries to demand collections 1. Went to Poonawala Fincorp NBFC call center in Pune — “couldn’t imagine place in the world where 300 people are shouting” 1. Understood that QC executive (20 of them) will fill in forms 1. “Wanted to move from cost center to revenue generation” — started as QC tool but realized collections is better 1. **Learnings** 1. Being first to collections is critical 1. “Promise To Pay” disposition doesn’t capture the full context of the call 1. Collections call analysis is the wedge 1. Now migrated to making the collections call 1. **GTM** 1. Spammed on LinkedIn — tried different copy 1. Nira Money — cold email 1. Jupiter, Groww — cold email as well...' WHERE id = 406 AND (agent_ids_notes IS NULL OR agent_ids_notes = '');
